flowchart TD
    Look[Visitor aims camera] --> Raycast[ArtworkInteraction raycasts]
    Raycast --> Hit{Artwork mesh hit?}
    Hit -- No --> Clear[Clear hover state]
    Hit -- Yes --> Hover[Set artwork hover]
    Hover --> Crosshair[Show interactive crosshair]
    Crosshair --> Click{Visitor clicks or taps action}
    Click -- No --> Continue[Continue exploration]
    Click -- Yes --> Select[App.selectArtwork]
    Select --> Context{Free exploration or tour?}
    Context -- Free --> Detail[Open detail modal]
    Context -- Tour --> Panel[Show locked tour panel]
    Panel --> Detail
    Detail --> Media[Image, audio, or video content]
